The following values are system-wide limits:

Shared memory limits

shmall : Maximum total shared memory in bytes
shmmax : Maximum shared memory segment size in bytes
shmmni : Maximum number of shared memory segments

Semaphore limits

semmsl : Maximum number of semaphores per array
semmns : Maximum total number of semaphores
semopm : Maximum operations per semop call
semmni : Maximum number of semaphore arrays

Message queue limits

msgmax : Maximum number of bytes in a single message
msgmnb : Maximum number of bytes in a single message queue
msgmni : Maximum number of message queues
